{"tid":878760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男抓鄰居的貓啪啪啪　女飼主看到後崩潰報警","createTime":"2018-10-27T11:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T20:24:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3ae10acf3422809f7e886754ff5f9d06825f3710","tid":878760,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T11:30:47.000Z","msg":"南非一名男子，抓了鄰居的貓後性侵牠，鄰居發現後超崩潰。<br />\n<br />\n據南非《TimesLIVE》報導，10月26日，德爾班一名男子性侵鄰居的貓，女飼主看到後立即打電話給保安公司，「她告訴值班的人說，她的鄰居正在跟她養的貓發生性關係」，保安公司的職員繼續說「這名女士走到她家旁，發現那個裸體的男子，用腳夾住了貓開始啪啪啪」。<br />\n<br />\n事發後，保安公司到場處理，並請動物保護協會前來處理受傷的貓，並將男子轉交給南非警方。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181027/640_165da5c35b43a425b7c07f42189b3615.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181027%2F640_165da5c35b43a425b7c07f42189b3615.jpg&h=0ca531a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男抓鄰居的貓啪啪啪　女飼主看到後崩潰報警。翻攝自《TimesLIVE》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.timeslive.co.za/news/south-africa/2018-10-26-man-arrested-after-allegedly-having-sex-with-a-cat/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timeslive.co.za%2Fnews%2Fsouth-africa%2F2018-10-26-man-arrested-after-allegedly-having-sex-with-a-cat%2F&d=B%2B%2BLgce60KlWlk4WYQb8eL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=08032b3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.timeslive.co.za/news/south-africa/2018-10-26-man-arrested-after-allegedly-having-sex-with-a-cat/</a><br />\n英文原文版"},{"pid":"ada321498c38af38c197c3e63badb0ff7bb63ea4","tid":878760,"uid":117200,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T11:33:44.000Z","msg":"人地拉個姦貓犯都出六個警察<br />\n香港個班直接掟走隻貓算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d994053c1b497f063d9abd3b8368a399710726","tid":878760,"uid":174418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T11:34:47.000Z","msg":"性病傳播"},{"pid":"eb41d27c4f8d612dab317a42aaaf2134807dd111","tid":878760,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":10,"